That's it for another series! What were your highlights? Let us know your best bits.

Thank you for all your support, and a special shout out to the wonderful crew behind the scenes that bring Salvage Hunters to our screens.

We'll be back with a brand new series in the new year! https://t.co/zuCemIYrZs

Salvage Hunters are setting their sights on amazing locations in Lincolnshire. There is no place the team won’t visit from salvage yards to private collections. So if you think you fit the bill or know somebody that does, then send us a DM and the team will get back to you! https://t.co/O08dKqb69M

BRAND NEW SALVAGE HUNTERS! It's the LAST EPISODE of the series - and of course it's a good one! Wherever you're watching, we hope you enjoy it.  Join us for Salvage Hunters, at 9pm on Quest

@DrewPritchard @Teeinavan @QuestTV @discoveryplusUK @findbyrebecca @ralphineson https://t.co/uAQsOANSwZ

TONIGHT! It's the last episode in the series. Drew & Tee head to salvage yard Spencer Architectural, which ends in a job for @NevBlacksmith. The boys travel south to Suffolk to dealer @southeantiques, ending the trip in Cheshire at the home of multiple dealers Farrow House https://t.co/raw2rvubjz
RT @DrewPritchard: New apprentice day @JohnnyVegasReal @Teeinavan @discoveryplusUK @QuestTV https://t.co/5bvBedaHbg

NEW SALVAGE HUNTERS: Tonight! Look no further than Quest at 9pm, it’s our penultimate episode of the series - make sure you tune in! 
@DrewPritchard @Teeinavan @QuestTV @discoveryplusUK @findbyrebecca @ralphineson https://t.co/ayy4GsuAX5

TONIGHT! Drew&Tee take up an exclusive invitation to a grand, Grade II listed mansion - Irnham Hall in Lincs. Heading south, the next stop is Devon to dealer Two Rooms. It's then onward to Norfolk, ending in a special invitation to a dealers personal collection at @antiques_holt https://t.co/tew87Z61fn

TONIGHT! Drew & Tee set their sights on the Isle of Wight. First stop is family run business Burfields Antiques, then to the storage barns of The Dairyman's Daughter in Newport. The trip ends in Ryde with an exclusive invitation to the island's oldest dept store, Elizabeth Pack https://t.co/TXxOwawkMy

It's nearly time for your favourite time of the week.. Make sure you clock on for a new episode of Salvage Hunters at 9pm on Quest!

@DrewPritchard @Teeinavan @QuestTV @discoveryplusUK @ralphineson @findbyrebecca @curvemediatv https://t.co/OtGDqN1omh

TONIGHT! @DrewPritchard & @Teeinavan are on the road to Yorkshire to the family run Heathcote Antiques, they head to Morecambe Bay for a seaside rummage at Bayside Emporium, ending this week's trip in St Albans at the eclectic barn of dealer @retrovation_ https://t.co/x0gt3wAO0M

TONIGHT! Drew&Tee take up an invitation to the home of rock fan & collector Peter, digging through his collection of rare music memorabilia. It's on to the capital to antique market @alfiesantiques, landing at the 17th Century cottage of a husband&wife dealer duo in North Wales https://t.co/QQaM6PCkFF

MID SERIES KLAXON! 🚨 Another BRAND SPANKING NEW episode of Salvage Hunters coming your way tomorrow night at 9pm. Rock music fan? You won't want to miss this one..🤘
@DrewPritchard @Teeinavan @QuestTV @discoveryplusUK @Bec_Pritchard @ralphineson @curvemediatv https://t.co/tWZ54ITngG

Salvage Hunters is on the hunt for locations for an upcoming episode in the North West of England. There is no place the Salvage Hunters team won’t visit from factories to fairgrounds. So if you fit the bill or know, then we want to hear from you!#salvagehunters https://t.co/B4q76uRMZk

TONIGHT! In another BRAND NEW episode of Salvage Hunters..@DrewPritchard  & @Teeinavan head to the West Country to let off some steam at @MineheadRailway, Drew goes on a spending spree at @TAVDevon, rounding off the trip at a stunning Somerset farmhouse with dealer @RalfesY https://t.co/G0W8TqdXZF

TONIGHT! Drew & Tee visit stoneware specialists Drakelow Barns Antiques, they make the journey East to Suffolk to the workshop of restorer and new contact Richard Rush, ending with a trip to a trio of Dudley dealers Lye, Pica & I.O.C Antiques
@DrewPritchard @Teeinavan @QuestTV https://t.co/dnmqWE3SMk

TONIGHT - @fredsirieix1 joins Drew & Tee on the road as they explore a beautiful manor house at @Wykenvineyards.
